New Records: Victor Wembanyama became just the third player in NBA history to record multiple 5x5 games
Key Match Events: Victor Wembanyama logged 25 points and nine rebounds
Chris Paul put up 19 points, seven rebounds, and 10 assists
Sandro Mamukelashvili scored 10 points on an impressive 4-for-5 shooting
Miscellaneous Highlights: The San Antonio Spurs delivered a statement win over the Utah Jazz, pulling out a 106-88 victory
The Spurs' bench added depth to their offense, allowing them to keep their offense rolling even when the starters rest
